      "author": "realhenrylan",
      "description": "## KiloCode for Obsidian v0.1.0\r\n\r\n### ✨ Features\r\n- 🤖 AI Chat Sidebar with streaming responses\r\n- 💬 Multi-tab chat with conversation history\r\n- 📝 Inline Edit with diff preview\r\n- 🔧 Slash Commands (`/compact`, `/clear`, `/model`, `/mode`)\r\n- 📎 @mention system for vault files, MCP servers, and subagents\r\n- 📋 Plan Mode (`Shift+Tab` toggle)\r\n- 🌐 MCP Server support\r\n- 🌍 i18n (English & Chinese)\r\n- ⚡ Virtual scrolling for performance\r\n\r\n### 📦 Installation\r\n1. Download `main.js`, `manifest.json`, and `styles.css` from this release\r\n2. Create folder `YourVault/.obsidian/plugins/kilocode/`\r\n3. Copy the files into the folder\r\n4. Enable the plugin in Obsidian Settings → Community plugins\r\n\r\n### 📋 Prerequisites\r\n- Obsidian v1.7.2+ (Desktop only)\r\n- KiloCode CLI: `npm install -g @kilocode/cli`",
